#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.171, sc5
#. VAR: phuṇamānassa → pūyamānassa (bj) | vuyhamānassa (si) | phusayamānassa (s1-3) | vuvahyamānassa (pts1) | punamānassa (?)
#. VAR: apavahati → apakassati (bj)
msgctxt "an8.10:5.1"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, mahato dhaññarāsissa phuṇamānassa tattha yāni tāni dhaññāni daḷhāni sāravantāni tāni ekamantaṃ puñjaṃ hoti, yāni pana tāni dhaññāni dubbalāni palāpāni tāni vāto ekamantaṃ apavahati. "
msgstr "Suppose that a large heap of grain is being winnowed. The grains that are firm and substantial form a heap on one side. And the grains that are flimsy and insubstantial are blown over to the other side. "

msgctxt "an8.10:5.2"
msgid "Tamenaṃ sāmikā sammajjaniṃ gahetvā bhiyyoso mattāya apasammajjanti. "
msgstr "Then the owners take a broom and sweep them even further away. "

msgctxt "an8.10:5.3"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu? "
msgstr "Why is that? "

msgctxt "an8.10:5.4"
msgid "Mā aññe bhaddake dhaññe dūsesīti. "
msgstr "So that it doesn’t spoil the good grain. "

