#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.172, sc7
msgctxt "an8.10:7.1"
msgid "Saṃvāsāyaṃ vijānātha, "
msgstr "By living together, know that "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.10:7.2"
msgid "pāpiccho kodhano iti; "
msgstr "they’re irritable, with wicked desires, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.10:7.3"
msgid "Makkhī thambhī paḷāsī ca, "
msgstr "offensive, stubborn, and contemptuous, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.10:7.4"
msgid "issukī maccharī saṭho. "
msgstr "jealous, stingy, and devious. "

# NOTE: BB has “calm”, apparently reading santavaco with MS text, but I prefer sanhavaco with PTS and Hare.
#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc8
msgctxt "an8.10:8.1"
msgid "Santavāco janavati, "
msgstr "They speak to people with a voice "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.10:8.2"
msgid "samaṇo viya bhāsati; "
msgstr "so smooth, just like an ascetic. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.10:8.3"
msgid "Raho karoti karaṇaṃ, "
msgstr "But they act in secret, with their bad views "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.10:8.4"
msgid "pāpadiṭṭhi anādaro. "
msgstr "and their lack of regard for others. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc9
msgctxt "an8.10:9.1"
msgid "Saṃsappī ca musāvādī, "
msgstr "You should recognize them for what they are: "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.10:9.2"
msgid "taṃ viditvā yathātathaṃ; "
msgstr "a creep and liar. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.10:9.3"
msgid "Sabbe samaggā hutvāna, "
msgstr "Then having gathered in harmony, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.10:9.4"
msgid "abhinibbajjayātha naṃ. "
msgstr "you should expel them. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc10
msgctxt "an8.10:10.1"
msgid "Kāraṇḍavaṃ niddhamatha, "
msgstr "Throw out the trash! "

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: apakassatha → apakassavā (s1-3) | avakassatha (mr)
msgctxt "an8.10:10.2"
msgid "Kasambuṃ apakassatha; "
msgstr "Get rid of the rubbish! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.10:10.3"
msgid "Tato palāpe vāhetha, "
msgstr "And sweep away the scraps—"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.10:10.4"
msgid "Assamaṇe samaṇamānine. "
msgstr "they’re not ascetics, they just think they are. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc11
msgctxt "an8.10:11.1"
msgid "Niddhamitvāna pāpicche, "
msgstr "When you’ve thrown out those of wicked desires, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.10:11.2"
msgid "pāpaācāragocare; "
msgstr "of bad behavior and alms-resort, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.10:11.3"
msgid "Suddhāsuddhehi saṃvāsaṃ, "
msgstr "dwell in communion, ever mindful, "

# NOTE: kappayavho is middle 2nd imperative pl, i.e. = -tha
#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.10:11.4"
msgid "kappayavho patissatā; "
msgstr "the pure with the pure. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.10:11.5"
msgid "Tato samaggā nipakā, "
msgstr "Then in harmony, alert, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.10:11.6"
msgid "dukkhassantaṃ karissathā”ti. "
msgstr "make an end of suffering.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an8.10:11.7"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an8.10:11.8"
msgid "Mettāvaggo paṭhamo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc12
msgctxt "an8.10:12.1"
msgid "Mettaṃ paññā ca dve piyā, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.10:12.2"
msgid "dve lokā dve vipattiyo; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.10:12.3"
msgid "Devadatto ca uttaro, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.10:12.4"
msgid "nando kāraṇḍavena cāti. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
